ceably slowed down. My hair feels stronger and looks thicker at the roots. Highly recommend.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5ghP2q_7G_text","label":"gg5ghP2q_7G_text","default":"<p>Alyssa M , Phoenix AZ</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkQ1vz9xK7_text","label":"ggkQ1vz9xK7_text","default":"<p>My hair was dry, dull, and breaking constantly. This shampoo brought back softness and shine. It actually feels nourished instead of stripped. I’m obsessed.<br><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggyZggFLNb_text","label":"gggyZggFLNb_text","default":"<p>Emily Johnson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggx3dH8QzZ9_text","label":"ggx3dH8QzZ9_text","default":"<p>“I noticed a visible reduction in hair fall after just a few washes. My hair feels stronger and healthier.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMaa8YDdyd_text","label":"ggMaa8YDdyd_text","default":"<p>Michael Anderson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-HgJLodju_text","label":"gg-HgJLodju_text","default":"<p>I was dealing with thinning hair, and this shampoo has definitely helped improve volume and texture.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzNdBBdCk4_text","label":"ggzNdBBdCk4_text","default":"<p>Olivia Brown</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglpV9s4qlu_text","label":"gglpV9s4qlu_text","default":"<p>love that it uses natural ingredients. My hair looks shinier and more manageable now.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggZBIC66cj_text","label":"gggZBIC66cj_text","default":"<p>Daniel Roberts</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYxF-TGbq9_text","label":"ggYxF-TGbq9_text","default":"<p>My hair feels much smoother and less prone to breakage since I started using this.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcNvSZAp2l_text","label":"ggcNvSZAp2l_text","default":"<p>Rachel P , Columbus OH</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxaXgr54n7_text","label":"ggxaXgr54n7_text","default":"<p>It’s rare to find a natural product that delivers results. The rosemary scent is clean and spa-like, and my hair feels stronger with every wash.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"}],
